{
  "stem": "14060.7",
  "chunk_idx": 3,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 3.6,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 33,
      "text": "So in comes a German-speaking supervisor of the camp, being an inmate himself.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 34,
      "text": "And they were like little [INAUDIBLE].",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 35,
      "text": "You know, you had to be worried.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 36,
      "text": "I'm talking of later days, when we realized what the setup was.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 37,
      "text": "And he went on to say that we have got machines-- which, in those days, one didn't know-- where we can put an x-ray through your shoes.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 38,
      "text": "And if you've got any valuables there or anything, give it now.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 39,
      "text": "Because we will test every shoe.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 40,
      "text": "And if one is found, you will be hanged immediately.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 41,
      "text": "That was the [INAUDIBLE].",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 42,
      "text": "That was the [INAUDIBLE].",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 43,
      "text": "Some people maybe did, some didn't.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 44,
      "text": "I don't know.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 45,
      "text": "We, we didn't even have any with us.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 46,
      "text": "But then when that was finished, they said, now, dismissed, meaning the end of the, of the action.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 47,
      "text": "And that is where you're going to sleep-- a concrete floor.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 48,
      "text": "There was literally room to stand next to each other.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 49,
      "text": "You could hardly sit down.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 50,
      "text": "I mean, you have to squat to sit down.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So that was the first afternoon experience of what it was.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "The next thing is-- right.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "What does one need most than anything else?",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "To go to the toilet.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "The order was that only 50 people can at one time go.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And if there are 48, they have to wait for another two till they're ready to, to go.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "You were not allowed to go either individually, pairs, or fives, or tens to go into the latrine, which was the so-called toilet.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "It wasn't English flush toilets.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "OK-- we get used to that.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Then, I don't think-- I can't remember if we got a little bit of bread or some rations that afternoon, certainly nothing warm.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "I mean, we were on the train a few days and all that.",
      "word_count": 13
    }
  ],
